trans-unit.source: The DsmlSoapConnection class is an abstract class that cannot be instantiated.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DsmlSoapConnection er en abstrakt klasse som ikke ikke kan startes.

trans-unit.source: It enables stateless and stateful protocols to be handled similarly by providing session-oriented features.
trans-unit.target: Muliggjør uten status og stateful protokollene som skal behandles på samme måte ved å formidle økten orientert funksjoner.

trans-unit.source: The DsmlSoapConnection constructor initializes a new instance of a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren DsmlSoapConnection initialiserer en ny forekomst av en <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The BeginSession method instructs the DSML server to start a new session.
trans-unit.target: Metoden BeginSession instruerer DSML-serveren til å starte en ny økt.

trans-unit.source: The method will block while waiting for a response from the DSML server and will timeout according to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden vil blokkere under venting på et svar fra serveren DSML og vil tidsavbrudd i henhold til den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A>

trans-unit.source: Thrown when a session is already open on the connection.
trans-unit.target: Et når en økt som er allerede åpen for tilkoblingen.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when the XML returned from the Server in response to the BeginSession is not well-formed.
trans-unit.target: Et når XML ble returnert fra serveren som svar på BeginSession ikke er riktig formet.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is a communications failure with the DSML server.
trans-unit.target: Et når det er en kommunikasjonsfeil med DSML-serveren.

trans-unit.source: The EndSession method ends the session with the DSML server and clears the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.SessionId*> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden EndSession avslutter økten med DSML-serveren, og fjerner den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.SessionId*>egenskapen.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.SessionId*>

trans-unit.source: The method will block while waiting for a response from the DSML server and will timeout according to the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Metoden vil blokkere under venting på et svar fra serveren DSML og vil tidsavbrudd i henhold til den <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryConnection.Timeout%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the DSML server terminates the session, a <xref:System.Net.WebException> is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Hvis DSML-serveren avslutter økten, en <xref:System.Net.WebException>forårsakes.</xref:System.Net.WebException>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.SessionId%2A> is still valid after the exception is thrown, the request never reached the server and the connection is still considered valid.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.SessionId%2A>er fortsatt er gyldige når den unntak, forespørselen nådde aldri serveren, og tilkoblingen er fortsatt gyldig.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.SessionId%2A>

trans-unit.source: Thrown when a communications failure occurs with the DSML server.
trans-unit.target: Et Hvis det oppstår en kommunikasjonsfeil med DSML-serveren.

trans-unit.source: Thrown when there is no open session.
trans-unit.target: Et når det er ingen åpne økt.

trans-unit.source: The SessionId property contains the active session ID.
trans-unit.target: SessionId-egenskapen inneholder den aktive økt-IDen.

trans-unit.source: A null value signifies no active session.
trans-unit.target: En nullverdi innebærer ingen aktive økter.

trans-unit.source: The active session ID.
trans-unit.target: Den aktive økt-IDen.

trans-unit.source: The SoapRequestHeader property contains the SOAP Header attached to outgoing requests.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen SoapRequestHeader inneholder SOAP-hodet som er knyttet til utgående forespørsler.

trans-unit.source: The API uses <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.BeginSession%2A> and <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.EndSession%2A> to track the lifetime of a session.
trans-unit.target: API-bruker <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.BeginSession%2A>og <xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.EndSession%2A>å spore levetiden for en økt.</xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.EndSession%2A> </xref:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DsmlSoapConnection.BeginSession%2A>

trans-unit.source: **Caution** Attaching an EndSession header to the SoapRequestHeader causes the API to become inconsistent with the connection and should be avoided.
trans-unit.target: **Forsiktig** tilknytting en EndSession-overskrift til SoapRequestHeader fører til at API blir ikke samsvarer med tilkoblingen og bør unngås.

trans-unit.source: The SOAP Header attached to outgoing requests.
trans-unit.target: SOAP-hodet som er knyttet til utgående forespørsler.
